Compilation and installation
============================

In order to compile prt you need following software packages:
	- GCC		>= 8.3
	- CMake		>= ...
	- Doxygen	>= ...	(optional)

To configure run:
	mkdir build
	cd build
	cmake .. -D ...

To compile and install run:
	make && make install


Information
===========

Mailing lists:
	...

For additional information about the project visit prt web site:
	https://prt.chinarulezzz.fun




Installing prt
--------------

## Requirements

- g++ >= 8.3 (C++17)
- pod2man (man pages)

## Compile

mkdir build
cd build

cmake .. \
	-DCMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX=/usr \

Note: add "-DCMAKE_BUILD_TYPE=Release" as cmake option
      to build non-debug version.

make -j$(nproc) all
make install
